inputs.prompt: A cinematic standoff inside a vast futuristic hangar drifting above a distant planet. Two men stand face to face at the center of the frame, frozen in a moment of raw tension. Their expressions are filled with restrained rage, jaws clenched, eyes locked. Cold blue rim light carves their silhouettes while warm amber warning lights flicker across metallic walls etched with wear and battle scars. Dust and tiny debris float in low gravity, catching beams of volumetric light. The camera angle is low and dramatic, emphasizing scale and dominance. Ultra-realistic materials, hyper-detailed faces, cinematic contrast, shallow depth of field, epic sci-fi atmosphere, high-end film still, 8K realism.
